          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>An <html:dfn>Inner Product Space</html:dfn> is a vector space <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[V]]></fr:tex> equipped with an <fr:link href="/vectsp-001Z/" title="Inner product" uri="http://localhost:8000/vectsp-001Z/" display-uri="vectsp-001Z" type="local">Inner product</fr:link>.</html:p>
